ROBEK is the registery of conditional approval and control.
Municipalities part of ROBEK must have the approval of the
registery to make valid decisions on loans and leases. The legality of
the budget decisions must be checked as well.
Fauske has a high amount of loan. The
economy is vulnerable to rent increases.
and they struggle with budget balancing.
High risk of ROBEK-membership.
